    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774700/extras/1ebb3cc7b27371f46d79edf8acce714d.poster.avif?t=1651966567\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774700/extras/1ebb3cc7b27371f46d79edf8acce714d.webm?t=1651966567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774700/extras/1ebb3cc7b27371f46d79edf8acce714d.mp4?t=1651966567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在 <strong>INVERT </strong>中，玩家将面临解决几个逻辑挑战的挑战。 您必须以有限的方式移动并使所有基地变为白色或所有基地变为黑色。 跳过基地时，相同的颜色会发生变化，您将利用这一点。<br>准备好迎接具有挑战性的体验，并在聆听平静而轻松的配乐的同时挑战自己。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774700/extras/b78f64736d56ae857e67a823fba5ad34.poster.avif?t=1651966567\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774700/extras/b78f64736d56ae857e67a823fba5ad34.webm?t=1651966567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774700/extras/b78f64736d56ae857e67a823fba5ad34.mp4?t=1651966567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>特征：<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>使用更改基色的机制使所有基色相同。<br></li><li>你的动作数量有限，给游戏玩法增加了一点挑战。<br></li><li>45 个难度级别从简单到困难的阶段。</li></ul>",
